      "span_text": "Aggressive surgical therapy needs excellent anesthetic support, and the study from Owusu-Agyemang et al.  examines the use of epidural analgesia in 215 adult patients undergoing HIPEC. This study used the practice of starting the epidural before the HIPEC and found a significant reduction in the blood loss and the fluid requirements of these patients.",
